        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks ADB for <hi rend="italic">Limulus</hi>.</p>  
<p>Does <hi rend="italic">Callithrix sciureus</hi> wrinkle the skin around its eyes when it screams? Do the eyes become suffused with moisture?</p> 
